videos.description: Matt Mooney passes to Tariq Owens who takes off to throw down an emphatic jam to start the game.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Owens opens the game with emphatic jam

videos.description: Jarrett Culver darts past the TCU defense to the rack for a layup to beat the halftime buzzer.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Culver makes buzzer-beating layup

videos.description: Alex Robinson lofts a lob in transition to Desmond Bane who bangs home a dunk to cap the break.
videos.headline: TCU's Bane catches lob pass and throws down a dunk

videos.description: Kevin Samuel catches the alley-oop pass from Kendric Davis and drops the hammer at the rim with a powerful two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Davis lobs to Samuel for big TCU dunk

videos.description: Tariq Owens catches the oop pass from Matt Mooney and pounds home a powerful dunk on a defender.
videos.headline: Owens smashes dunk on defender

videos.description: Tariq Owens comes up with a massive block and Davide Moretti throws a lob on the break to Jarrett Culver for the monster jam.
videos.headline: Huge Owens block leads to Culver monster jam

videos.description: The TCU defense falls apart as Jarrett Culver drives to the rack to throw down a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Culver breezes by the TCU defense for two-handed jam
